<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
<style>

     *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        body {
            
            font-size: 36px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222;
        }

        h1{
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;

        }
     /* layout */
     .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f0f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .email-body{
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .email-footer{
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
        }
</style>

</head>
<body>
    <section class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Hello <%= name %>, </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="email-body">
           <p> A new reply has been added to your question in the video <%= title %>, </p>
           <p> login to view it and continue the conversation</p>
           <p>Thank you for being a part of the community</p>
        </div>

        <footer class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:enitanpeters28@gmail.com">enitanpeters28@gmail.com</a></p>
        </footer>
    </section>
</body>
</html>